item.title: SoftLayer_Network_Storage_Backup_Evault
item.description: SoftLayer_Network_Storage_Backup_Evault Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Network_Storage_Backup_Evault contains general information regarding an EVault Storage service such as account id, username, maximum capacity, password, Storage’s product type and the server id. Local accountId The internal identifier of the SoftLayer customer account that a Storage account belongs to. Type: integer capacityGb A Storage account's capacity, measured in gigabytes. Type: integer createDate The date a network storage volume was created.
